

## Your Learning Path

After Fibonacci, we'll move into more interview-oriented topics:

1. ✅ Functions
2. ✅ Strings (20+ problems)
3. ✅ Lists (25+ problems)
4. ✅ Tuples
5. ✅ Dictionaries
6. ✅ Sets
7. ✅ File Handling
8. ✅ Exception Handling
9. ✅ OOP in Python
10. ✅ Modules & Packages
11. ✅ NumPy
12. ✅ Pandas
13. ✅ AI-focused Python (PyTorch, Hugging Face, LangChain)

By the end, you'll be writing Python confidently for AI and technical interviews.
